### Disable / Enable Resource
```yml
pcs resource disable fs_gfs2 --wait=5
pcs resource enable fs_gfs2 --wait=5
```
### Disable / Enable Cluster
```yml
pcs property set maintenance-mode=false
cluster stop --all
cluster start --all
```
### Update Resource
```yml
pcs resource update fs_gfs2 directory="/oldcommon"
```
### Rsync
```yml
rsync -avhp -v  --exclude={'*.log.*','*.zip*','*.tar*','*.dump*',LOGS/*,LARSH/*,DOWNLOAD_FILES/*,DOWNLOAD/*,BACKUP_LOGS/*} /common/ /backup
```
